###2. Content details for each page:

This website is called **Dreamy Delight Ice Cream**, and it will include all topics learned this semester in <ins> CIS 130</ins>. 

**Home page** (index.html) will introduce the website and offer an overview of the website. It will include a hero section,
featured ice cream flavors, and a mission paragraph that reflects both the brand and the objectives.

**Menu page (menu.html)** will show different ice cream flavors of the store using images and styled layout sections.
This page will demonstrate CSS layout techniques such as Flexbox or Grid learn in week 4 and will be designed to be visually engaging and 
responsive.

**About Us page** (about.html) will explain the purpose of the website, and it will also reflect more on what was learned during the course.

**Contact page (contact.html)** will include a contact form use with form spree and show accessibility design practices. It will allow customers to 
type their name, email, phone number, and message.

