###7.	Code Validation Plan:
All code will be validated using web standards tools:

**HTML Validation:**
•	W3C HTML Validator used on every page
It will check missing tags or structural errors.

**CSS Validation:**
•	W3C CSS Validator used for stylesheet checks  
It will check Invalid properties and syntax errors in the code.

**WAVE Validation:**
It will check Missing Alt text on pictures, low or high colors contrast issues, ARIA errors, and accessibility alerts and warnings.

